<chapter id="chapter-configuration">
  <title>Configuration</title>

  <para></para>

	<section>
	  <title>Dependencies</title>

	  <para>Make sure your include the plug-in in your project. If you are using
	  Maven, add the following dependency to your pom:</para>

	  <example>
		<title>OpenStreetMap layer dependency</title>

		<programlisting>&lt;dependency&gt;
	  &lt;groupId&gt;org.geomajas.plugin&lt;/groupId&gt;
	  &lt;artifactId&gt;geomajas-layer-openstreetmap&lt;/artifactId&gt;
	  &lt;version&gt;1.7.0&lt;/version&gt;
  &lt;/dependency&gt;</programlisting>
	  </example>
	</section>


  <section>
    <title>OpenStreetMap layer configuration</title>

